twitch_info.title: I Wanna Make a Sandwich - Any% Speedrun in 1:23:37
twitch_info.description:
Get the game here - [https://delicious-fruit.com/ratings/game_details.php?id=12411](https://delicious-fruit.com/ratings/game_details.php?id=12411)
Pretty good run. Unfortunate freeze I got on a screen transition in Metroid cost about a minute, and some boss deaths a little more. Quite happy with it though!
